{"id":"5ac5137b-9781-4acd-9bbb-72380ef68c86","name":"\"Thank goodness we aren't alone...\"","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 126, 255);\">\"What is that?\" </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 156, 252);\">\"Kinda looks like a Monkey!?\"</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 255, 251);\">\"A Monkey....\"</span><br><br><img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/wWX7upr7SvwAAAAM/byuntear-cat.gif\" alt=\"Cat Laugh GIFs | Tenor\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(167, 246, 243);\">\"MONKEEEYYY!?? PFFTT!?!?!?\"</span><br><br>1SNORE:<br><br>You first get into the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 250, 195);\">backrooms </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 161, 248);\">Twilight</span>, <span style=\"color: rgb(175, 252, 255);\">Rainbow</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(241, 173, 231);\">Pinkie</span> find you<br><br>2 SORK<br><br>You been here for awhile...<br><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 255, 176);\">Fluttershy</span> Rarity and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 214, 164);\">Applejack</span> find you in the <span style=\"color: rgb(195, 205, 255);\">PoolRooms</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 205, 255);\">3 NORK</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 205, 255);\">Your own</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 205, 255);\">Also a few levels I added</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">LEVEL 0–9 — The “Standard Levels”</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 1 — The Habitable Zone</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Concrete hallways, flickering lights, industrial ambiance, machinery noises. Survivable. Has supplies.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 2 — Pipe Dreams</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Hot, claustrophobic tunnels with pipes. Extremely dangerous. Entities patrol constantly.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 3 — Electrical Station</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Tight corridors, loud electrical hums. Contains many dangerous entities. Flickering lights everywhere.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 4 — Abandoned Office</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Empty office floor with working furniture, stable electricity, and water sources. Minimal entities.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 5 — The Hotel</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">A large ornate hotel stuck in the 1930s. Carpeted halls, ballrooms, and music. Heavily haunted.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 6 — Lights Out</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Pitch-black hallways. The darkness itself behaves like an entity. No light works.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 7 — The Flooded</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">A vast ocean with a single platform. Something massive lives beneath the waves.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 65, 138);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 187, 187); color: inherit;\">Level 8 — The Cave System</mark></span></p><p><span style=","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"jBiDIbseVw_Lc_hUqfO9h.webp","creator":"Car_47","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🦄 Non-human","👭 Multiple","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":1523,"messages":21700,"created_at":"2025-06-30T17:41:11.174179+00:00"}